<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>bèi qiú guī lái 迦南279</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 nǐ cóng bèi qiú zhī de shèng lì guī lái
 gěi wǒ men yī gè jīng xǐ kāi mén zǒu jìn lái
 wǒ men duō me gāo xìng wàn fēn gǎn kǎi
 jǐn jǐn wò zhù nǐ de shǒu xīn zhōng shén me dōu míng bái
 shòu jǐn le mó nán nǐ méi yǒu shī bài
 xiàng hán dōng lǐ de méi huā ào shuāng xuě shèng kāi
 rén shēng dōu huì yǒu yù dào láng qún de shí hòu
 nà shí nǐ yào xiǎng dào shén yǔ nǐ tóng zài
 jiǎo xià shēng huī fàng guāng cǎi.</lyrics>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>279</hymn_number>
</song>